snippet.title: The Round // Gameplay Preview - VALORANT
snippet.description:
More info on our website: 
https://PlayVALORANT.com

VALORANT is Riot Games' upcoming 5v5 character-based tactical shooter. This alpha gameplay footage was captured from an internal developer playtest - pardon the video quality, we hope you appreciate the gameplay. If you like what you see (or hear), come play in Summer 2020. 

Follow us on Twitter: 
https://twitter.com/PlayVALORANT 

Follow us on Instagram: 
https://www.instagram.com/PlayVALORANTofficial

We're going to link our YouTube for the hell of it, even though you're here already. Maybe subscribe if you're reading this far: 
https://www.youtube.com/PlayValorant
